# Task Management Application

## Overview

This project is a simple Task Management Application developed using React.js, Node.js, and Express.js. It allows users to add and manage tasks through a user-friendly interface.

## Features

* Create Tasks
* View Tasks
* Simple and Responsive Interface
* Backend API using Express.js

## Technologies Used

* React.js
* Node.js
* Express.js
* JavaScript
* VS Code

## Project Structure

task-manager/
├── backend/
│   └── server.js
├── frontend/
│   └── App.js
└── README.md

## How to Run

### Backend

1. Open terminal
2. Navigate to backend folder
3. Run:
   node server.js

### Frontend

1. Navigate to React project folder
2. Run:
   npm start

## Output

* Backend runs on: http://localhost:5000
* Frontend runs on: http://localhost:3000

